data.description: Motivated Seller willing to offer Closing Cost Assistance. This beautiful 2-story 2,505 sq. ft home offers 4 bedrooms, a den, 2.5 baths and a spacious 2-car garage. The premium lot showcases an extended covered front porch, extra long drive way and a massive backyard. This open floor plan, offers a well-appointed kitchen upgraded with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. The flexible room on the lower level currently functions as an office but can easily be converted. Both the owner's suite and the second upstairs bath boast double vanities. This home also offers the convenience of an upstairs laundry room. Community amenities include 2 large pools, clubhouses, an exercise room, tennis and basketball courts and much more
